pwstaa: Nceda ushintshishe isikhathi ngemuva kwezifundo ezisemthethweni ezishintshile.
t1: Lesi sici sihumusha ngokushesha futhi kalula izigaba zombhalo kolunye ulimi.
t2: Lesi isici esithuthukisiwe sokuhumusha esiskena futhi sihumushe umbhalo usuka ezithombeni, okwenza kube lula kubasebenzisi ukuqonda okuqukethwe ngolimi abaluncamelayo.
t3: Lesi sici sinikeza ukunethezeka okukhulu ngokuhumusha izingxoxo zesikhathi sangempela phakathi kwezilimi ezahlukene.
t4: Lesi sici siwubuhlakani bokwenziwa obunolwazi mayelana nezindawo zokuvakasha, izindawo ezikhanga izivakashi, amahhotela, ukudla, njll. Sisebenza njengomsizi obalulekile ngokunikeza ulwazi oluwusizo nezincomo kubathandi bokuvakasha.
t5: Lesi sici sihlanganisa izihloko zezokuvakasha zakamuva kuhlelo lokusebenza, okuvumela abasebenzisi ukuthi bafunde izindaba lapho beziphumulele. Bazokwazi ukufinyelela ukwaziswa kwamuva ngezihloko ezihlobene nokuvakasha.
t6: Lesi sici sikuvumela ukuthi uhlole izimo zezulu zanamuhla kanye nezinsuku ezi-5 ezilandelayo zedolobha. Sinikeza ulwazi mayelana nesimo sezulu samanje nesizayo.
t7: Lesi isici esilula kakhulu sokuskena amakhodi e-QR ukuze uthole izixhumanisi, imininingwane ye-WiFi, ukudluliselwa kwemali, njll. Sithuthukisa ulwazi lomsebenzisi ngokunikeza ukufinyelela okulula kumasevisi ahlukahlukene nolwazi.
t8: Lesi sici sibonisa ulwazi lomsebenzisi futhi sikuvumela ukuthi uliphathe futhi ulihlele ngokuqondile.
t9: Lesi isikrini esikhulu esethula inhloso yephrojekthi kanye namalungu abandakanyekayo ekusetshenzisweni kwayo.
t10: Lesi sici sikuvumela ukuthi ulinganise izici ngaphakathi kohlelo lokusebenza ngokwakho. Sicela usazise uma unezikhalazo noma imibuzo.
t11: Lesi sikrini sifingqa izici nokusebenza kohlelo lokusebenza Olukhululekile Lolimi futhi sinikeza izincazelo ezinemininingwane yesici ngasinye ukuze sisize abasebenzisi baqonde kangcono uhlelo lokusebenza.

conntentour: Siyiqembu labafundi abenza izifundo zobunjiniyela besofthiwe e-FPT Can Tho University futhi lolu hlelo lokusebenza luwumphumela wephrojekthi yethu yokuthweswa iziqu. Sakha isicelo sokusekela ezokuvakasha ngokusebenzisa izinhlaka ezitholakalayo nama-API. Sisebenzisa uhlelo lwethu lokusebenza, ingenza umhlaba ube ngcono. Ungakwazi ukuhlola kalula, unqobe izithiyo zolimi, futhi uhlangabezane ngokugcwele nempilo yamasiko amaningi.

contentfpt3: Ihlinzeka ngezinhlelo zokuqeqesha ezisezingeni eliphezulu, eziklanywe ngokuvumelana namamodeli okuqeqesha amazwe ngamazwe.
